%N A392965 Least number of vertices in a stepwise-irregular tree with at least one vertex of degree n.
%H A392965 Ivan Gutman, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.amc.2017.12.045">Stepwise irregular graphs</a>, Applied Mathematics and Computation 325 (2018), 234-238.
